= ResourceView

Resource View is a simple extension of resource_controller (by James Golick) to drying up basic views: index, show, new, edit, _form.


== Features

- Customize any view without workarounds;
- Dont cover all the cases; 
- That's all!


== Get it

If you yet didn't install resource_controller, install it:
script/plugin install git://github.com/giraffesoft/resource_controller.git

Install resource_view as plugin:
script/plugin install git://github.com/lucasdecastro/resource_view.git


